author: pburba
msg: On the issue-3334-dirs branch: Follow-up to r35667, remove some uneccessary
code and clarify a comment.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/update_editor.c
(schedule_existing_item_for_re_add): Clarify a comment that really
needed it.  Don't set the 'deleted' entry field of the parent of a
re-added tree.  Why I did this in the first place is a complete mystery.
Was it a cut-and-paste error?  Too much glue sniffing?  TC brain rot?
Let that be a lesson to you kids: Write the comment when you write the
code.  If they don't match, be worried.
